changeDesc.p: Transcoded from a MusicXML version 3.0 file using an XSLT stylesheet (musicxml2mei v. 3.0).
SC und RS haben die Codierung nach OA korrekturgelesen und entsprechend angepasst.
Converted to MEI version 4.0.0 using mei30To40.xsl, version 1.0 beta
corrected label and labelAbbr

convert tupletSpans to tuplets; utilizing convert.tupletSpan.xsl
several corrections, especially regarding ties and tuplets
